{"store": "ah", "scraped_at": "2026-06-25T13:55:03.085803+00:00", "external_id": "123209", "raw": {"card": {"webshopId": 123209, "hqId": 42962, "title": "AH Elstar zak", "salesUnitSize": "1,5 kg", "unitPriceDescription": "prijs per kg €1.53", "images": [{"width": 800, "height": 800, "url": "https://static.ah.nl/dam/product/AHI_484a746a76526b595467714a78763078316c6d524677?revLabel=1&rendition=800x800_JPG_Q90&fileType=binary"}, {"width": 400, "height": 400, "url": "https://static.ah.nl/dam/product/AHI_484a746a76526b595467714a78763078316c6d524677?revLabel=1&rendition=400x400_JPG_Q85&fileType=binary"}, {"width": 200, "height": 200, "url": "https://static.ah.nl/dam/product/AHI_484a746a76526b595467714a78763078316c6d524677?revLabel=1&rendition=200x200_JPG_Q85&fileType=binary"}, {"width": 48, "height": 48, "url": "https://static.ah.nl/dam/product/AHI_484a746a76526b595467714a78763078316c6d524677?revLabel=1&rendition=48x48_GIF&fileType=binary"}, {"width": 80, "height": 80, "url": "https://static.ah.nl/dam/product/AHI_484a746a76526b595467714a78763078316c6d524677?revLabel=1&rendition=80x80_JPG&fileType=binary"}], "bonusStartDate": null, "bonusEndDate": null, "discountType": null, "segmentType": null, "promotionType": null, "bonusMechanism": null, "currentPrice": null, "priceBeforeBonus": 2.29, "orderAvailabilityStatus": "IN_ASSORTMENT", "orderAvailabilityDescription": null, "mainCategory": "Fruit, verse sappen", "subCategory": "Zakken", "brand": "AH", "shopType": "AH", "bonusPeriodDescription": null, "availableOnline": true, "isPreviouslyBought": false, "descriptionHighlights": "<p>Elstar is het populairste handappeltje van Nederland. Deze friszoete appel met fijn cassisaroma is bovendien een echte alleskunner: heel geschikt voor appelmoes, appelsap en appeltaart.</p><p><ul><li>Smaak: zoetzuur</li><li>Bereiden: de appel wassen en eventueel schillen</li><li>Bewaren: appels na aankoop bewaren in de koelkast</li><li>Geschikt voor: snack, bakken, salade</li></ul></p>", "propertyIco